<br></br>386 Harehills Lane 
<br></br>Leeds 
<br></br>LS9 6NF 
<br></br>
</p></div></div>

<h2 id="lost-damaged-or-stolen-permits">Lost, damaged or stolen permits</h2>

<p>Contact <abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency">DVSA</abbr> straight away if you lose or damage a permit, or if one is stolen.</p>

<p>You should also <a href="https://www.gov.uk/contact-police" class="govuk-link">tell the police</a> if a permit is stolen.</p>

<p><strong><abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency">DVSA</abbr> International Road Haulage Permits Office</strong><br></br>
<a href="mailto:irhp@dvsa.gov.uk" class="govuk-link">irhp@dvsa.gov.uk</a><br></br>
Telephone: 0330 678 1117<br></br>
Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm<br></br>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/call-charges" class="govuk-link">Find out about call charges</a></p>

<h2 id="if-you-give-up-your-operator-licence">If you give up your operator licence</h2>

<p>Send your <abbr title="European Conference of Ministers of Transport">ECMT</abbr> permits and log books to <abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency">DVSA</abbr> if you <a href="https://www.gov.uk/manage-vehicle-operator-licence" class="govuk-link">apply to give up (‘surrender’) your vehicle operator licence</a>.</p>

</div>
</div>


